Guests: North Carolina Republican Congressman Patrick McHenry, Ranking Member on the House Financial Services Committee, Tim Carney, Author of “Alienated America,” Senior Political Columnist at the Washington Examiner and Resident fellow @ the American Enterprise Institute, Al Mottur, Democratic Strategist and Partner at Brownstein, Hyatt, Farber & Schreck and Hagar Chemali, CEO of Greenwich Media Strategies and former Treasury spokesperson for Terrorism and Financial Intelligence.
